## About Team Phantom Forge

Team Phantom Forge, representing Dreams of Bangladesh, develops next-generation 
flood management robotic vehicles to support human rescue and water resources 
management. This project is part of our participation in the 7th World Invention 
Competition and Exhibition.

### Our Mission
"To encourage the next generation to dream big and believe in their power to create change."

### Contact
- Organization: Dreams of Bangladesh
- Email: team@phantomforge.bd
- GitHub: https://github.com/tamimhossain11/PHANTOM_FORGE
- Location: Bangladesh


